# YourStageSkybox Commands
yourstageskybox.command.usage=/yourstageskybox <set <name> [alpha] [duration] [player] [dim] | clear [player] [dim] | alpha <value> [player] [dim] | duration <sec> [player] [dim] | info [dim] | list | reload>
yourstageskybox.command.set.usage=/yourstageskybox set <name> [alpha] [duration] [player] [dim]
yourstageskybox.command.alpha.usage=/yourstageskybox alpha <0.0~1.0> [player] [dim]
yourstageskybox.command.duration.usage=/yourstageskybox duration <seconds> [player] [dim]
yourstageskybox.command.set.success=§aSet skybox §e%1$s§a for %2$s in dimension §e%3$d
yourstageskybox.command.clear.success=§aReverted to vanilla sky for %1$s in dimension §e%2$d
